br.octahedron.cotopaxi.cloudservice.common
Class DistributedQueue<T>

java.lang.Object
  br.octahedron.cotopaxi.cloudservice.common.DistributedQueue<T>

public class DistributedQueue<T>
extends Object

A data structure based on FIFO (First In, First Out) criterion using a Memcache service, to store elements, and some extra functions. All operations that modify this queue (add, remove and removeElements) are thread-safe.
